        desc: "web3.py is the dominant Python EVM library. Brownie is dead (deprecated 2023). Ape (eth-ape) is the modern Python smart-contract dev framework with plugins. For frontend / TypeScript apps, viem (or ethers.js) is the standard — Python is usually backend / indexer / bot.",
